    <h2>Student Ministry Spiritual Transformation Process</h2>
    <p>Shiloh students will be encouraged to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Reach out towards God through prayer and Bible study.</li>
        <li>Connect to God, the Church, their family, one another, and the community by joining the Shiloh Student Ministry.</li>
        <li>Grow in God by using the tools necessary for students to develop Spiritual H.A.B.I.T.S.</li>
        <li>Discover God in their lives by identifying their S.H.A.P.E. to use their gifts and abilities for ministry.</li>
        <li>Honor God through worship.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>If you have any questions, concerns, or an interest in joining or serving in Shiloh's Youth Ministry, please call Rev. Donald Jones, Youth Pastor, at 646-8653.</p>
    
