    <h3>Shiloh Missionary Baptist Church Mission & Vision</h3>
    <p><strong>Mission Statement:</strong> Our mission is to preach, teach, and live the redeeming love of God to a lost, but changing world.</p>
    <p><strong>Vision:</strong> Our vision is to become a Biblically functioning community of believers who are fully devoted to Jesus Christ.</p>
    <h3>Shiloh Student Ministry Mission & Vision</h3>
    <p><strong>Mission Statement:</strong> Our mission is to involve middle school and high school students in the life of the church and to reach out to the unchurched in our community.</p>
    <p><strong>Vision:</strong> Our vision is to spiritually form the lives of middle school and high school students and to equip them to become devoted followers of Christ.</p>
    
